briefdescription.para: File C++ (associated to Stock_Write_Dynspec_Metadata_Part.h) for stock and write metadatas for the ICD6's Dynspec Groups.

detaileddescription.para: Overview: Functions stockDynspecMetadata and writeDynspecMetadata are described (programmed) here. The first one (stockDynspecMetadata) will take as parameter all Dynspec Group's metadata and stock them in the private attributes of the class object. The second function (writeDynspecMetadata) will write them in the hdf5 output file (in the corresponding dynspec).
